Common.Highlight.Common.Text: RENTAL RATE: $17.00 per square foot, NNN
YEAR BUILT: 1989
TOTAL RENTABLE AREA: 111,514 SF
TYPICAL FLOOR SIZE: Approximately 27,300 SF
METHOD OF MEASUREMENT: BOMA, 15% multi-floor factor
NUMBER OF FLOORS: Four floors plus lower level
MANAGEMENT: ORG Property Management
ELEVATORS: Two (2) passenger elevators
PROPERTY UPGRADES: The Building has recently undergone significant renovations throughout all common hallways and men’s and women’s restrooms (which now feature touch-less fixtures and dispensers)

ELECTRICITY + HVAC: Roof mounted, gas fired make-up air unit with MERV 15 filtration supplies tempered and filtered air to water source heat pumps throughout the building. Water Source Heat Pumps make up the zones throughout the building. Gas fired boiler and cooling towers maintain the water loop temperature that the water source heat pumps use for heating and cooling. Temperatures controlled by individual thermostats per zone and the building energy management system.
PARKING: Ample surface parking spaces are available; underground parking available in the lower level of the building, on an as available basis.
INTERNET: The Building offers high speed Fiber Internet service from AT&T and Spectrum.

BUILDING AMENITIES: Completely renovated workout facility (locker rooms, showers, new equipment). New lounge/snack area completely renovated, outdoor lounge/dining seating, building conference room, perimeter walking path around a one-acre lake, two-story lobby with lake views.
